'''H'Kak beans''' grew on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. They were gathered from [[H'Kak bush]]es and were easily found due to their intense orange [[Color/Legends|color]]. Harvested beans were used to create [[Tatooine H'Kak bean tea]].

